	  pihwm - A lightweight C library for Raspberry Pi hardware modules
	  =================================================================


New in the current development tree
===================================

The code is restructured to use a standard configure, make, make install build
sequence.

Known issues:

There is currently no test suite.


New in release 0.0.1
====================

A first release prepared for the UK Open Source Hardware User Group (OSHUG)
camp on 15/16 September 2012.

Provides basic library functions for gpio and i2c.
